OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,FITV's Ella Robinson reports from
OL,7,FBolton where the council have been
OL,8,Ftackling homelessness
OL,10,FNine of Bolton's most vulnerable
OL,11,Fhomeless people have a new home this
OL,12,Fwinter.
OL,14,FThe council has built self-contained
OL,15,Fpods on a car park near the town
OL,16,Fcentre. The pilot follows a similar
OL,17,Fscheme which launched in Blackburn
OL,18,Fduring the pandemic.
