OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,FThe cabins may be small, but they are
OL,7,Fwarm, and have a bed, bathroom, desk
OL,8,Fand a separate communal kitchen.
OL,10,FAnd for their new residents, they've
OL,11,Fbeen life-changing.
OL,13,FCarol, not her real name, moved in
OL,14,FNovember, just before the temperature
OL,15,Fdropped to minus 7 degrees.
OL,17,FShe had been sleeping on the streets
OL,18,For staying in a friend's van after she
OL,19,Flost her home that she had been living
OL,20,Fin for 10 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
