OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,FIt was the first time she had ever
OL,7,Fbeen homeless and she was drained from
OL,8,Fworrying about winter and how she was
OL,9,Fgoing to stay warm. Then she was
OL,10,Foffered one of the new sleeper pods.
OL,12,F"It has been a but of a godsend to be
OL,13,Fquite honest with you," she said.
OL,15,F"It's a temporary basis for the winter
OL,16,Fmonths so we're not freezing to death
OL,17,Fon the streets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
