PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1767184583
OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,F"With the weather being as horrendous
OL,7,Fas it has been, we're just grateful
OL,8,Fthat we've got a roof and it's warm,
OL,9,Fand it's just brilliant."
OL,11,FThe most recent rough sleeper count
OL,12,Fsaid Bolton had 41 people sleeping on
OL,13,Fthe streets in September.
OL,15,FBolton council say each person who has
OL,16,Fbeen homeless for three months or more
OL,17,Fcosts the NHS #4,300, mental health
OL,18,Fservices #2,100 and the criminal
OL,19,Fjustice system #12,000, so not only
OL,20,Fwill this make a huge difference to
OL,21,Fpeople's lives, it will save money too.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
