OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,FCouncillor Sean Fielding, the
OL,7,FExecutive Member for Adults and
OL,8,FCommunity Housing at Bolton Council
OL,9,Fsaid: "We've seen a rise in
OL,10,Fhomelessness right across the country,
OL,11,Fnot just here in Bolton.
OL,13,F"But that's a product of
OL,14,Funderinvestment in the kind of
OL,15,Fservices that would prevent people
OL,16,Ffrom getting that bad in the first
OL,17,Fplace over the last 10-15 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
