OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1767184583
OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,F"Things are starting to change but
OL,7,Fit's going to take a lot of time and
OL,8,Fwe will need some temporary measures
OL,9,Flike this in the interim until we can
OL,10,Fbuild the homes that we need and get
OL,11,Fpeople off the streets."
OL,13,FAs well as providing somewhere warm to
OL,14,Fsleep, the pod residents will also
OL,15,Freceive support for mental health and
OL,16,Fsubstance abuse issues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
