OL,3,CFormer rough sleeper calls new pods 'a
OL,4,Cgodsend'
OL,6,FCouncillor Sean Fielding said: "The
OL,7,FSleeper Pods will hopefully provide a
OL,8,Fstepping stone for some of our most
OL,9,Fvulnerable citizens to rebuild their
OL,10,Flives."
OL,12,FThe pods will be open until 31 March.
OL,13,FThen the council plan to review the
OL,14,Fpilot and see if it can be used
OL,15,Felsewhere.
